  m_text: "You were created to destroy our enemies, but now you have turned against
    your creators.\nIf you want to escape the laboratory, you will have to kill everyone
    in your way.\nHowever, be careful: every bullet you fire, every trap you set,
    may destroy you yourself.\nAs the saying goes: don\u2019t dig a pit for someone
    else \u2014 or dig one, but then don\u2019t fall into it yourself\u2026 or something
    like that."
